[Adapted from the online novel,
The Age of Wind and Rain]

3
00:00:09,810 --> 00:00:14,780
[Episode 22]

4
00:00:15,920 --> 00:00:17,640
Yun Lian, you witch.

5
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:19,440
How dare you seduce Dongfeng?

6
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:21,440
