114
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:08,360
Looking at such a beauty,
how can I not be hasty?

115
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,480
Chairman Deng.

116
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:12,880
Doing opium business is a capital crime.

117
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:16,560
Can you ensure everything goes smoothly?

118
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,960
Since you heard about me from Miss Qin,

119
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:22,000
you should know my relations
with Commander Qin.

120
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,720
Commander Qin is a big shot.

121
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,080
He's afraid of nothing.

122
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:29,920
But I'm a nobody.

123
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,520
How can I compare with him?

124
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,120
As long as you're with me,

125
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,920
you won't have to fear anything.

126
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:43,400
So, how long have you been working
with Commander Qin?

127
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:45,680
It's been six or seven years.

128
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:54,320
Can you offer me the same price
as Commander Qin?

129
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:58,920
Miss Shen, do you really come here
for business?

130
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,360
Of course.

131
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,800
In that case,

132
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,320
you need to sweeten the deal, got it?

133
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,280
Miss Shen, do you really come here
for business?

134
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,600
Of course.

135
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,120
In that case,
you need to sweeten the deal, got it?

136
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,680
Then forget it.

137
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,880
Quite feisty.

138
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,840
Quite feisty.

139
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:24,720
Come here.

140
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,760
What are you doing?

141
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,800
Let go of me.

142
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,160
Let me go.

143
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,720
Stop it, Dongfeng.

144
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,080
Don't kill him!

145
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,680
Are you alright?

146
00:08:57,640 --> 00:09:01,720
Doing opium business is a capital crime.

147
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:05,000
Can you ensure everything goes smoothly?

148
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,440
Since you heard about me from Miss Qin,

149
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:10,120
you should know my relations
with Commander Qin.

150
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,800
Once we make it public,

151
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,680
he will be ruined and notorious.

152
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,520
Very soon,

153
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,640
everything will settle down.

154
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,800
After it's all over,

155
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,200
what do you want to do?

156
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,160
Go back to school.

157
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,560
I'll complete my studies.

158
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:53,560
I'll go with you.

159
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:58,880
We can experience the journey
we've taken again

160
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:02,160
and see the scenery we enjoyed together.

161
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:07,800
The street
outside our school is beautiful.

162
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,400
I often dreamed about it.

163
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,760
I wonder if it has changed.

164
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,880
Dongfeng.

165
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:28,920
Dongfeng.

166
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,320
Are you back?

167
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:33,840
Dongfeng?

168
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
Dongfeng.

169
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:40,560
Strange. I heard a voice.

170
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,640
Dongfeng.

171
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:18,230
♪I'm waiting for the rain
to wet the city♪

172
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:21,430
♪At dusk♪

173
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:25,990
♪As I ran into someone I missed
at the street corner♪

174
00:11:26,070 --> 00:11:29,510
♪Old memories flashed♪

175
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:33,110
♪If I can shout that I miss you♪

176
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:37,110
♪I'll be waiting for the sunshine
in the rain♪

177
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:43,710
♪If your heart is as cold as ice♪

178
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:48,750
♪My heart will call for you♪

179
00:11:48,830 --> 00:11:52,550
♪Are you as resolute as I am?♪

180
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:56,510
♪You wake me up to see you♪

181
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:59,750
♪I'm sure your heart will be softened♪

182
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:03,380
♪You approach me in the name of love♪

183
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:07,550
♪As time goes by, I realize
there's no time like the present♪

184
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:12,630
♪I have no regrets when being with you♪

185
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:15,270
♪And you're like the rising wind♪

186
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:18,830
♪I ask you not to leave me
in the name of love♪

187
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:23,750
♪The wind blows
and we part ways in silence♪

188
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:25,990
♪You're like a cloud♪

189
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:30,540
♪Sometimes close, sometimes distant♪
